{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_01","textHome":"我是在名叫杜鹃之家的孤儿院被养大的，@在那之前的事情我都已经不记得了。因为都是@1岁时候的事情了，况且我还是被人抛弃。@好像是在拉面店后面丢弃的鸡骨旁被发现的。@很过分对吧……不过，我倒是很喜欢拉面的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_18","textHome":"我最近，在做一个很大的雕刻。啊……不过@已经不能算是刻了吧，感觉差不多是削。@因为我在用电锯做！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_19","textHome":"这样子我一定是变强了对吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_20","textHome":"我懂了我懂了！有些……不一样的感觉呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_21","textHome":"我从以前开始就是这样，心里想的要么立马@说出来，要么就会体现在表情上，一直都@改不过来……不过，这也算是我的特点吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_22","textHome":"对我来说，养育我的老师就如同真正的母亲@一样。温柔，总是挂着笑容，我最喜欢她了。@但是，她已经不在人世了……所以，@我要连同老师的份一起活下去才行！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_23","textHome":"在我一个人无精打采的时候，木叶和叶月……@还有杜鹃花之家的大家总是在鼓励我……@对我来说，他们就如同家人一样。所以，@我要为了我的家人打起精神！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":302800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302850,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_50_24"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302850,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":302850,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302850,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json